<br>
People are always camping/soloing the Seafury Cyclopses and Ancient Cyclops spawn there, and they drop cyclops toes sometimes.  Gornit, near the Pirate camp on Seafury Island drops all three kinds of giant toes (he's some kind of freak), and people are always camping him because he drops as much as 50 plat every 6 minutes.<br>
<br>
You'll probably get all your toes for free.<br>
<br>
Baron Yadeezh Minionmaster<br>
