I know this is posted elsewhere, but don't forget that Gornit in OOT drops ALL FOUR kinds of toes. So join a plat-camping group on Gornit... usually no one cares about the toes he drops. Or when my lower level mage was finishing garg hunting, he would shout and over 2 days people we nice enough to give all for free, since giant varient toes are NOT no drop.<br>
